question:
Give the expected major product of reaction of 2,2-dimethyloxacyclopropane with each of the following reagents.

(a) Dilute $H_2SO_4$ in $CH_3OH$​

(b) $Na^{+-}OCH_3$ in $CH_3OH$  

(c) Dilute, aqueous $HBr$

(d) Concentrated $HBr$ 

(e) $CH_3MgI$, then $H^+$, $H_2O$

(f) $C_6H_5Li$, then $H^+$, $H_2O$
